data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. BACK ON MARKET DUE TO BUYERS FINANCES** Spacious 1,695. square foot 3 Bedroom 2 Bath with NEW ROOF 2021, NEW A/C 2017. Hickory model for sale in Stonecrest. Beautiful Updated Kitchen w/center island and Quartz Countertops, large pantry & breakfast bar and Newer Stainless Steel appliances! Tile throughout the main areas of the home with carpet in the bedrooms. Enclosed premium acrylic Florida room. Beautifully landscaped. Tray ceilings in both the dining room & the master bedroom. Master suite has a walk-in closet, and the master ensuite bath features double sinks & a large low-step shower. Generator plug to the breaker box is already installed for you and the garage service door is being replaced by the sellers. Stonecrest is an upscale gated 55+ community that offers resort style amenities such as 27 holes of golf, 4 pools (2 heated), tennis, pickleball, softball, fitness center, state of the art community center with many clubs & lots of activities all included in the low monthly HOA fee except golf. Make plans to see this fine home today!
